The crux of this issue is hinted at in the [log4j-jms.properties file|http://svn.apache.org/repos/asf/activemq/trunk/assembly/src/release/example/src/log4j-jms.properties], to avoid a circular dependency, activemq cannot log to the jms appender:
{code}
## Be sure that ActiveMQ messages are not logged to 'jms' appender
log4j.logger.org.apache.activemq=INFO, stdout
{code}
